data.description: LOCATION & STUNNING RENOVATIONS!! This home has it all! You must see to appreciate the many TOP QUALITY UPGRADES in this versatile tri-level home. New Roof in 2018, New AC and Hot water Heater in 2021, New Sprinkler System with Automatic Timer, All New Plumbing and Electric in 2021! The Oversized Kitchen is a Chef's dream with Granite Countertops, matching backsplash and New Softclose Shaker Style Cabinets. New Stainless Steel Appliances added in 2021 include: Induction Flat Cooktop, Microwave/Convection Oven, Smart Refrigerator, with Stainless Steel Vent Hood. You will LOVE the wall to wall Glass Room in the rear of the home that could be used as a HUGE Familyroom, Mancave, or Flex space for multiple uses! Enjoy 2 Master bedrooms, with the main Master bedroom on the lower level that has been transformed into an Owners Private Quarters with a master en-suite bathroom boasting floor to wall GORGEOUS White & gray accent TILE, modern accents throughout including a Freestanding Soaking Tub, Dual sinks with Waterfall Faucets, Gray Shaker Style cabinets with a HUGE walk-in shower and Barn Door leading to the OVERSIZED Master Closet. The stairs have waterproof laminate flooring leading to the 3 additional bedrooms including a 2nd Master suite with master bathroom and a nice size walk-in closet. This home boasts a WIDE OPEN floorplan with the Kitchen in the center of it all, with plenty of space for Family gatherings, with a large open Formal dining room. Gorgeous White & gray accent tile flooring seamless throughout the kitchen, dining room and formal living area. Smart Home features include: Bluetooth Lighting throughout including Bluetooth speakers in the Bathrooms, Electrical Patio Door with remotes, new Front Door with modern safety features. The Garage has been converted to an office with over 400 square feet of space, you could create part of this area into a workout space/Gym or even create a 5th bedroom! The possibilities are endless.   Outside, the nearly one acre of land offers a feeling of privacy, peace and tranquility as you drive down the long extended concrete driveway through the Automatic Electrical Gate, the property has a private vinyl fence with a HUGE Concrete area for additional parking as well as parking for 2 RV's and a Concreted area for the BRAND New Studio Guest House located in the backyard with it's own brand new septic tank. Also, this property is configured for 2 RV's as it has TWO 30 AMP Hook-ups, one for each RV and even a Dumping Station! There is a Firepit for family outdoor gatherings and plenty of room for the family to spread out and enjoy the Florida weather on this unique property with so many upgrades, you have to tour this STUNNING property to appreciate it!   The location of this home is perfect for a small business owner, on a super-sized CORNER lot on Kings Ave., across from Kingswood Elementary School, the property could easily be converted to commercial for endless opportunities. Situated in the heart of Brandon, close to restaurants, shopping areas and entertainment with easy access to HWY 301, HWY 60, I-75 and the Crosstown Expressway. To the west, it's about a one hour drive to the best Gulf Coast beaches and the Orlando theme parks to the east. Hurry this one won’t last – request a private showing today!
